page.title: 08Life Styles
page.content: My name is Lee.I am eleven years old.I live in Harold Hill and I am in the fourth year at St Ursula's School.Iget up at 6.30 a.m have my breakfast get dressed and watch breakfast T.V..I sometimes walk my dog.School begins at 8.50.We say prayers and then do our handwriting and English.At 10.10 we have play time,at 10.55 we do Maths.Lunch is from 11.55 until 1.25 I have school lunch (salad,hot dog and yogurt).At 1.30 we do Creative writing at 2.30 we have Art or Games.My favourite subject is model building.School ends at 3.30 and I have my tea at 4.00.I go out to play from 4.30 until 6.30 when I do my homework.When I finish my homework I watch T.V. until I go to bed at 9.30.
